   <mrv:ManagementsReview contextRef="c0" xml:lang="da">&lt;p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;
&lt;span style="vertical-align: inherit;"&gt;
&lt;span style="vertical-align: inherit;"&gt;Main activities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;br/&gt; 
&lt;em&gt;The company's main activity remained to purchase and sale of sneakers&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt; 
&lt;strong&gt;
&lt;span style="vertical-align: inherit;"&gt;
&lt;span style="vertical-align: inherit;"&gt;Development in activities and financial conditions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;br/&gt; 
&lt;em&gt;At the end of 2024, leading into early 2025 there was an attempt to revitalise the company's activities but only a single sale was made, following early Jan the company made no sales and went inactive in business.
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt; It has been decided that the company is to be closed, and hence all remaining obligations were settled over the course of the year with the intention of closing the business via self declaration&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;  &lt;/p&gt;</mrv:ManagementsReview>
